  <brief_title>Comparison Study of Two Splints Used for Treatment of Acute Temporomandibular Pain.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Clinical Trial on the Treatment Effectiveness of Two Splints for Acute Temporomandibular Pain.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
